==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outlet
<hw>Out"let`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The place or opening
by which anything is let out; a passage out; an exit; a vent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Receiving all, and having no <qex>outlet</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outlet</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Outlet
<hw>Out*let"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To let out; to
emit.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Daniel.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outlie</ent>⟦br⟧
